  {
    "row": 42,
    "rowsha": "5jBdL+XQMl9rjrygJw2tu1qie6X1+p40uihWvi3KYDE=",
    "originContent": "Basic flow:",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 43,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "1. 서비스를 시작합니다: `docker compose up -d`"
  },
  {
    "row": 44,
    "rowsha": "9neW0kr3wDUCb9yLLzPi1ovxZFgvudvog8mBpjl5Gp4=",
    "originContent": "1. Start the service: `docker compose up -d`",
    "translatedContent": "2. 컨테이너 내부에서 인증합니다: `docker compose exec tailscaled tailscale up`"
  },
  {
    "row": 45,
    "rowsha": "qxAVVivO3GAg7ZX8tvIkXkk/YOtYQV8k+be1J0y1cV8=",
    "originContent": "2. Authenticate inside the container: `docker compose exec tailscaled tailscale up`",
    "translatedContent": "3. AWG 명령어를 동일하게 실행합니다, 예를 들어: `docker compose exec tailscaled tailscale awg sync`"
  },
  {
    "row": 46,
    "rowsha": "t6rWpd0sUkGPMwLXkoEc15IKNPS5lFpuRfkhQNX4UgY=",
    "originContent": "3. Run AWG commands the same way, for example: `docker compose exec tailscaled tailscale awg sync`",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 47,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "Headscale을 사용하는 경우, `tailscale up`에 `--login-server https://your-headscale-domain`을 추가하세요."
  },
  {
    "row": 48,
    "rowsha": "18imqI4uEHxFwibA2PP5k8vEqO0JNbFLvO0tUWrPkUg=",
    "originContent": "If you use Headscale, add `--login-server https://your-headscale-domain` to `tailscale up`.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 49,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "선택적 호스트 별칭:"
  },
  {
    "row": 50,
    "rowsha": "MY1ZYUxWgDYMnUHszfjLa8szFroX+/Z3BCtLdGN/slg=",
    "originContent": "Optional host alias:",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
